---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<section class="px-4 bg-[#5c2e4a] pt-50 pb-10 relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-50">
    <svg class="w-full h-50" viewBox="0 10 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <pattern id="circles" x="0" y="10" width="10" height="30" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
        <circle cx="5" cy="8" r="8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-orange-500"></circle>
      </pattern>
      <rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(#circles)"></rect>
      </svg>
    </div>


  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-tight">VALORIZAMOS A<br>CRIATIVIDADE COM DIREÇÃO.<br>POTENCIALIZAR IDEIAS,<br>PARA CRIAR CONCEITOS<br>VISUAIS QUE COMUNICAM<br>COM IMPACTO.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300 mb-6">Amplificar ideias, emoções e experiências através do design. Transformamos conceitos em imagens que falam por si, conectando marcas e públicos através de narrativas visuais que deixam impacto, que transcendem e impressionam entre marcas e públicos.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-xl">▶</div>
          <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-medium">KEY VISUAL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-xl">▶</div>
          <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-medium">CENOGRAFIAS</span>
        </div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-xl">▶</div>
          <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-medium">CENGRAFIA</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-xl">▶</div>
          <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-medium">EDITORIAL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-xl">▶</div>
          <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-medium">MERCHANDISING</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>